---
title: KitaitiShop
pagination:
  data: item
  size: 1
  alias: product
permalink: 'item/{{ product.url | slugify}}/'
layout: layout.njk
path: ../../css
---
    <header class="header">
        <h1 class="header__title">{{ title }}</h1>
        <ul class="header__nav">
            <li class="header__list"><a href="../../index.html"class="header__link">TOP</a></li>
            <li class="header__list"><a href="../../about/index.html" class="header__link">ABOUT</a></li>
        </ul>
    </header>

    <div class="item">
      <div class="item__inner">
        <div class="item__box">
          <div class="item__bisual">
            <img src="../../images/{{ product.url }}/{{ product.itemphotos[0]}}" alt="itemのメイン画像" class="item__img">
            <div class="item__img-box">
              <img src="../../images/{{ product.url }}/{{ product.itemphotos[0]}}" alt="" class="item__slide">
              <img src="../../images/{{ product.url }}/{{ product.itemphotos[1]}}" alt="" class="item__slide">
              <img src="../../images/{{ product.url }}/{{ product.itemphotos[2]}}" alt="" class="item__slide">
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="item__content">
            <h1 class="item__title">{{ product.name }}</h1>
            <h3 class="item__price">¥{{ product.price }}</h3>
            <p class="item__text">{{ product.text }}</p>
            <ul class="item__detail">
              <li class="item__list">■品番<span class="item__span ml">{{ product.id }}</span></li>
              <li class="item__list">■カラー<span class="item__span">{{ product.colors }}</span></li>
              <li class="item__list">■サイズ<span class="item__span">{{ product.size }}</span></li>
              {% if product.state === true %}
              <li class="item__list item-box">■数量<input type="number" class="item__count" name="count"></li>
              {% endif %}
            </ul>
            {% if product.state === true %}
            <input type="button" class="item__in" value="カートに入れる">
            {% endif %}
            {% if product.state === false %}
            <input type="button" class="item__in" value="Sold Out">
            {% endif %}
            <ul class="item__attention">
              <li class="item__matter">※発送は注文日から一週間ほどかかる場合がございます。</li>
              <li class="item__matter">※お問い合わせは各種SNSからお問い合わせください</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <footer>
        <div class="footer">
            <div class="footer__inner">
                <div class="footer__box">
                    <img src="../../images/other/instagram.png" alt="インスタグラムのアイコン" class="footer__img">
                    <img src="../../images/other/line.png" alt="ラインのアイコン" class="footer__img">
                    <img src="../../images/other/twitter.png" alt="ツイッターのアイコン" class="footer__img">
                </div>
                <small class="footer__copy">&copy;2022KitaitiShop</small>
            </div>
        </div>
    </footer>
    
    <script src="../../js/style.js"></script>